      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "UK stolen vehicle recovery firm Tracker warns the latest statistics from police indicate a sharp "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            8
          ],
          1,
          "increase in thefts"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          ". The company says partly what’s fueling this problem is the lack of new cars as factories shut down. Even now that many have reopened, they’re not at full operating capacity."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "Partly what’s holding up vehicle production is parts suppliers who haven’t ramped up production again. Criminals are seeing an opportunity as supply dwindles but demand doesn’t. The plan is to "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            9
          ],
          1,
          "steal cars"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
